CVE-2026-56131
CVE-2026-56407
CVE-2026-56408

# c-ares CVE in Alpine base image — DNS resolver library.
# Frontend container uses nginx for static file serving, does not make outbound DNS queries.
# Review date: 2026-07-11
CVE-2026-33630

# curl/libcurl CVEs in Alpine base image — SMB connection reuse + cookie leak.
# Frontend container only serves static files via nginx, does not make outbound
# curl/SMB/cookie requests. Will resolve when Alpine updates curl to 8.20.
# Review date: 2026-07-14
CVE-2026-5773
CVE-2026-6276
